Food Products

Company Overview of Sime Darby Plantation Sdn Bhd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sime Darby Plantation Sdn Bhd engages in oil palm and rubber plantation management, cultivation, and downstream activities, as well as agribusiness and food, and research and development activities. Its upstream operations include development of oil palm plantations, cultivation of oil palm, management of estates, cultivation of rubber, milling of fresh fruit bunches (FFB) for crude palm oil (CPO) and crude palm kernel oil; and downstream activities comprise manufacturing and distribution of oils and fats, oleochemicals, and palm oil-based biodiesel, as well as fast moving consumer goods for food, non-food, and agribusiness customers. The company also engages in research and development oper...
Sime Darby Plantation Sdn Bhd engages in oil palm and rubber plantation management, cultivation, and downstream activities, as well as agribusiness and food, and research and development activities. Its upstream operations include development of oil palm plantations, cultivation of oil palm, management of estates, cultivation of rubber, milling of fresh fruit bunches (FFB) for crude palm oil (CPO) and crude palm kernel oil; and downstream activities comprise manufacturing and distribution of oils and fats, oleochemicals, and palm oil-based biodiesel, as well as fast moving consumer goods for food, non-food, and agribusiness customers. The company also engages in research and development operations focusing on sequencing, assembling, and annotating oil palm genome. It trades and markets palm products, such as FFB, CPO, crude palm olein, refined bleached deodorised palm olein and oil, refined bleached deodorized palm stearin, palm fatty acid distillate, and palm acid oil products; and lauric products, including palm kernel, crude palm kernel oil, refined bleached deodorized palm kernel olein and oil, refined bleached deodorised palm kernel stearin, and palm kernel fatty acid distillate products in Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia, Thailand, Vietnam, Japan, China, Hong Kong, Germany, the United Kingdom, South Africa, the Netherlands, Canada, and the United States. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia with additional offices in Jakarta, Indonesia; and Chennai, India. It has up stream operations in Malaysia, Liberia, and Indonesia. Sime Darby Plantation Sdn Bhd operates as a subsidiary of Sime Darby Berhad.
Detailed Description


