Sime Darby

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Sime Darby Berhad





Type

Publicly traded government-linked company


Traded as
MYX: 4197


ISIN
MYL4197OO009


Industry
Conglomerate


Predecessor
Sime Darby
Guthrie
