Overview








About:
Sime Darby Energy & Utilities (E&U) is the engineering and utility arm of the larger Malaysian-based multinational, Sime Darby Group. Our core businesses are in Trading, Engineering & Technical Services, Ports & Logistics and Water Management.Guided by practical optimism to make a difference in the businesses we are in, we are determined to drive our aspiration, ?Engineering Sustainable Solutions? by making it a reality for all.Today, Sime Darby Energy & Utilities Non-China operations are represented by its Trading and Engineering & Technical Services business units in Malaysia, Singapore and Thailand, while its operations in China are represented by the Ports & Logistics and Water Management business units in the province of Shandong, People?s Republic of China. We are supported by a strong and dedicated team of approximately 2,000 people throughout our operations.
Sector: Oil & Energy
Website: http://www.simedarbyenergyutilities.com/
Year Established: 

